{"tid":761582,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無可能有一日人類淪為家畜","createTime":"2018-07-30T13:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T14:22:05.000Z","uid":36134,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4c051faa6d23573045048549bb71633c9c9d53be","tid":761582,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:31:08.000Z","msg":"其實呢個世界都係弱肉強食<br />\n人類將部分智商差距太大既動物馴化成家畜（尤其識群居）<br />\n圈養佢地 將佢地作為食糧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果有一日 有超高智商外星人黎到<br />\n將人類整個文明摧毀<br />\n圈養所有人類<br />\n不出幾代 人類後代缺少社教化同智能發展<br />\n人類可能會喪失左文字同語言<br />\n甚至徹底淪為家禽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每次一諗起自己呢個想法都覺得不寒而慄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcbc1ee86c91d2fcca49d51bc5a264a16e42b1db","tid":761582,"uid":67551,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:38:43.000Z","msg":"而家地產商咪圈養緊啲人喺劏房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nassume人類被人食 個問題就低質晒了<br />\n而家窮撚日日校鬧鐘起身幫有錢人搵錢，仲OT冇錢補，好過做食物"},{"pid":"c6941fe156e182986dc7bdde2351f4a426718a2b","tid":761582,"uid":28547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:40:36.000Z","msg":"冇 回本期太長"},{"pid":"39a8253e388a0387ffb6dec0bfde69014d17bcce","tid":761582,"uid":161260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:48:57.000Z","msg":"養人類做乜<br />\n十幾年先食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701d4a1cb9ffc12253d54ece691a58a9d612b9e1","tid":761582,"uid":71913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"39a8253e388a0387ffb6dec0bfde69014d17bcce","tid":761582,"uid":161260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:48:57.000Z","msg":"養人類做乜<br />\n十幾年先食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"你食唔食乳豬？"},{"pid":"07f5ea3566a5fa50e01d2e6c3b8da019efeca8a5","tid":761582,"uid":14073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:01:29.000Z","msg":"有機會，所以人類要凌駕其他生物，幫動物講説話嘅都係人奸"},{"pid":"409de3dcd3d33e0b0bd7691beba34e0f23a20c76","tid":761582,"uid":7840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:17:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c88c147a0fee3399c89b856296105b7cc2df3b73","tid":761582,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:22:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}